reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 31, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This table is adorable! It was super easy to put together and it's a pretty nice size with storage underneath. I ordered this for my daughter's nursery, and it is a sturdy & cute table. I would definitely recommend getting this table! We had looked at a bunch that were great but super expensive!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 12, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars For the price, this is pretty good! Comes with Allen wrench required to assemble
reviews.reviewText: First off, this was very easy to assemble. It took me only 5-10 minutes by myself. Secondly, it feels pretty sturdy. The feet on the bottom seem level with one another so there’s no wobble. I love when furniture like this comes an Allen wrench or whatever tools you need. It had all the required screws and a bag with a couple extras and the required Allen wrench. All the screws with different heads were easy to tell apart and all the pieces were labeled. The instructions were easy to follow.Aesthetically speaking, I think it looks nice for the most part. I ordered the white and beige, and the white paint job on the top isn’t the highest quality ever but it’s really not that noticeable. You have to be looking at it from a certain angle in certain lighting to notice that it’s not the highest quality paint job. It kind of looks like they painted it with Kilz and called it a day. It could have used one more coat. But the surface is smooth and doesn’t seem scratched. I’ll also be putting things on top of this table, so it really won’t be noticeable.Getting to some smaller details, I attached a picture of the basket and it is able to hang down with about a 1 inch gap between the bottom of it and the legs. I think this looks nicer rather than having the basket wrinkle up and be cramped in the space provided.The only thing I see being an issue with this design, however is that if you put anything heavy in the basket, over time, I think the support rods for the basket will gradually wear at the fabric and possibly cause a hole. I only plan on keeping a lap blanket or something light in the basket anyway. The basket also has a structured base. I’d say the bottom of the basket feels more sturdy than cardboard, however, not quite as hard as real wood. Maybe it’s a thin MDF board?Overall, for 40$, this is a pretty good end table and much more sturdy than a lot more expensive pieces I’ve bought online before.Also, if you order this and it looks like Piece B won’t line up with Pieces C and D- it will. Just look it like a clock and screw in at 12:00 and 6:00, then screw in at 9:00 and 3:00.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 14, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Suprised by the quality!
reviews.reviewText: This table looks great! Easy to put together and is very sturdy. I wasn't expecting the quality to be as good as it is because the table is so inexpensive. The tabletop and basket are large and can hold several items.

This is a really cute side table and fits perfectly between our two lazy boys in our basement TV room. The table was super easy to assemble and us sturdy too. The cats like to use the bottom as a bed, but that was expected. Lol!
Bought this for my toddlers big girl bedroom. The colour is great and the basket for the bottom is perfect for little stuffed animals.
Easy to put together & looks exactly as pictured. I love it!

This side table is definitely as attractive as its photos and I love the storage underneath! I’m not sure if it could hold the 77lbs it says it can but it makes a great accent piece. The basket feels good quality. Very minimal wobble, the feet definitely help. All pieces were labelled and instructions were simple.The only two downsides I noticed are- When you attach the metal ring to the table top, the pre-drilled holes don’t line up perfectly with the holes in the metal ring, so the screws want to go in crooked. You may have to fiddle to get a good fit.- I also noticed this table blemishes very easily. If you tighten the screws into the table top even a little too snug, tiny little cracks appear in the wood/paint next to the hole. Table came with small marks in the paint on the edge of the table top.
I love this nightstand. Its a beautiful pink and looks modern and unique. Very cute for nursery room!! Love the storage bin in the bottom.
